screen_desc:
The screenshot shows the Amazon Shopping app interface on a mobile device. At the top, there is a search bar with the text "Search or ask a question." Below it, there are various product categories including "Beauty essentials," "Keep shopping for Laptop stands," "Recommended deal for you," and "Glow up under $25." 

A pop-up message in Vietnamese appears, asking for permission to record audio with the options:
- "Trong khi dùng ứng dụng" (Allow while using the app)
- "Chỉ lần này" (Only this time)
- "Không cho phép" (Don't allow)

ui_elements.text: Cho phép Amazon Shopping ghi âm?
ui_elements.content_desc: "Permission message asking to allow Amazon Shopping to record audio"
